WALTER MCLEAN, M.P., travel to Tokyo, New Delhi, Lusaka, Harare, Windhoek, Maputo and Rome for the period of January 19 to Feburay 11, 1990 to speak to the United Nations Seminar on Far Eastern Action Against Apartheid and to lead the Canadian Delegation to the Southern Africa Coordination Conference.
